LCCCTA strives to meet the needs of our tennis community by:
Providing youth tennis programs and camps
Coordinating local league play
Providing equipment assistance for schools and community programs
Advocating for public facility improvements
Offering social tennis events
Board meetings are held monthly and all members of the community are invited to attend.
Be sure to check our
online event calendar
for upcoming dates and times. We hope to see you there!

About
Learn more about our not-for-profit, volunteer-based community tennis association.
Our Mission
To promote and grow the sport of tennis in Lake City and Columbia County, Florida by providing accessible, inclusive, and engaging programs that inspire a lifelong love for the game. Through education, community engagement, and sportsmanship, we strive to create opportunities for players of all ages and skill levels to develop their abilities, build meaningful connections, and enjoy the benefits of an active lifestyle.

Our Vision
Through education, community involvement, and competitive opportunities, we strive to foster a love for tennis, encourage healthy lifestyles, and build a strong, connected tennis community in Lake City and Columbia County, Florida. We are eager to see a tennis facility built to both grow the game of tennis in our community, and to serve as a tournament facility hosting local, regional, and national tennis tournaments.

Core Values
We believe tennis is a lifetime sport that contributes to good health, character and responsible citizenship.
We believe in providing opportunities for everyone to participate, regardless of skill, age, physical ability, gender, ethnic ethnicity, economic background, or sexual orientation.
We believe that our mission can best be achieved through teamwork with staff, volunteers, community advocates, and strategic partners working together to advance our mission.
We believe in being good stewards of our financial and human resources and creating clear value in all that we do.
We believe in a fun, positive culture that values new ideas and methods, without fear of failure.
